query:
SELECT pi.id, pi.productId, pi.url, pi.isPrimary, p.name 
FROM product_images pi 
JOIN products p ON pi.productId = p.id 
WHERE p.categoryId = 1 
ORDER BY p.id, pi.isPrimary DESC;
